         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot. Garden ¶ 19/6/70 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to inform you, that the Audit-Commissioners have asked me to adjust the advance, which was made for gravelling at Toorak in 1867, a duty whi...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.06.19</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To William Odgers<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">W70/6809, unit 467, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne bot. Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">19/6/70</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to inform you, that the Audit-Commissioners have asked me to adjust the advance, which was made for gravelling at Toorak in 1867, a duty which I then undertook on behalf of the Lands Department.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>For background, see M to J. Grant, 9 August 1867 (in this edition as 67-08-09a),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and M to Hemry C. Manners-Sutton, 9 August 1867.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The expenditure is in reality long ago adjusted, but the adjustment has seemingly yet to pass through some official form. For this the papers, which were<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(— as far as I am aware —)<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>transmitted to the Department of the hon. the Chief Secretary,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M has added a marginal note at this point, marked by an asterisk: '29 June 1868'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>are needed, and I beg therefore to enquire, whether these documents are still accessible at your Office, and could be sent to me, with a view of fulfilling the requirements of the audit commissioners.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        </seg>The files were at the the Lands Office, and were forwarded to M in response to M to E. Agg, 21 June 1870.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller, M.D.,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Direct. botan. Garden.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Undersecretary</p>
         </div>
